{"tid":155893,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"釘宮四萌終於完晒","createTime":"2017-03-14T11:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T09:37:52.000Z","uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a22018e5d3e0a5ea96e8ebde1deb04066d5a9a82","tid":155893,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T11:15:00.000Z","msg":"《旋風管家》將於4月12日完結 釘宮四萌至此全部完結<br />\n<br />\n由畑健二郎創作的漫畫《旋風管家》從2004年開始在日本雜誌《周刊少年Sunday》中連載，到現在都已經連載了13年了，此前也曾改編過TV動畫和真人電視劇，近日，官方透露了《旋風管家》將於4月12日完結的消息，不少媒體感嘆「釘宮四萌至此就全部完結了」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n零使最終卷上個月出左，今次到旋風管家4月完結 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f286467ea1c9ad11ce6c2c9429e830853165c75d","tid":155893,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_WU2wcpWvRPk/TGFoSuIerWI/AAAAAAAACQw/vrJqtWD_gqg/s1600/%E6%BC%AB%E8%BF%B7%E3%80%8C%E7%88%BD%E5%93%A5%E3%80%8D%E6%9A%B4%E7%B4%85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F_WU2wcpWvRPk%2FTGFoSuIerWI%2FAAAAAAAACQw%2FvrJqtWD_gqg%2Fs1600%2F%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%2588%25BD%25E5%2593%25A5%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%259A%25B4%25E7%25B4%2585.jpg&h=27021460&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5fa7fe0b36637c8b1f0bde75319c0bf01a9f19e","tid":155893,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T11:20:27.000Z","msg":"至少仲有神樂"},{"pid":"f145b3e6efd1523f78c66a09588a9747021cfc43","tid":155893,"uid":50194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T11:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d498ce431a6208645329c637befa7e9afbc174a","tid":155893,"uid":29442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T08:33:37.000Z","msg":"爆笑管家終於肯完<img src=\"/asse